we have analyzed the various models of organization growth,

01:33:36.500 --> 01:33:41.000
we have discussed what the life cycle of an organization is

01:33:41.500 --> 01:33:44.000
and how different forms of changes

01:33:44.500 --> 01:33:48.000
manifest in this life cycle of an organization,

01:33:48.500 --> 01:33:52.000
we have analyzed the influence of the human factor

